==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: duō xíng bù yì bì zì bì
===Proverb===
'''[[多]][[行]][[不]][[義]][[必]][[自]][[斃]]'''
# The wages of sin is death; He who is unjust is doomed to destruction.
